headline: Fortinet to Announce Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024 Financial Results
summary: SUNNYVALE, Calif., Jan. 02, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- News Summary Fortinet® (NASDAQ: FTNT), the global cybersecurity leader driving the convergence of networking and security, announced that it will hold a conference call to discuss its fourth quarter and full year 2024 financial results on Thursday, February 6, at 1:30 p.m. Pacific Time (4:30 p.m. Eastern Time).
